[I] A size-optimized STL implementation

[T] USTL is a partial implementation of the Standard Template Library which
[T] reduces code size by factoring memory management code into a non-template
[T] base class and deriving containers from it.

[U] https://ustl.sourceforge.net

[A] Mike Sharov <msharov@hotmail.com>
